{"tid":2401871,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"YouTuber Jennie 更新頻道啦！帶大家走入《THE SHOW》幕後，BLACKPINK 隊友也入鏡","createTime":"2021-02-10T05:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T01:25:58.000Z","uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7368ec80db681d02fd040f5397862fb83fb7eebe","tid":2401871,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_823146619226cf586b35371363ed4073/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-10/133632-896728.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_823146619226cf586b35371363ed4073%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-10%2F133632-896728.png&h=42051b5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不到一個月就吸引 500 萬人訂閱的「最強 YouTuber」BLACKPINK Jennie 剛剛終於上傳第二支影片，大家都看過了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n時隔三個星期，Jennie 在今天（10 日）終於在自己的 YouTube 頻道上傳了第二支影片，維持第一支影片精簡的節奏，以短短 4 分多鐘的內容介紹準備 BLACKPINK 首場線上演唱會《THE SHOW》時的日常點滴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vH3EhJFY3us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvH3EhJFY3us&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQjQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=4a004358\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vH3EhJFY3us</a><br />\n<br />\n相較於第一支影片，這支 &ldquo;THE SHOW vlog&rdquo; 從開場、剪接節奏到都顯德更加成熟，以恰到好處的步調揭開 Jennie 練舞、彩排《THE SHOW》、和成員一起拍畫報的有趣過程，最後還跑了片尾字幕「在準備 THE SHOW 時，跟很好的人一起留下了開心的回憶，真的很幸福。謝謝各位舞者姊姊、哥哥和工作人員！也謝謝久等的 BLINKs。」<br />\n<br />\nJennie 的 YouTuber 誕生於她今年的生日當天，一公開就在全世界引發熱烈迴響，隔天立刻吸引近 200 萬人訂閱，本月 3 日也迅速地跨過「500 萬訂閱」這個驚人的里程碑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_29455640b909b92876afa276db4a0fe9/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-10/133632-896729.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_29455640b909b92876afa276db4a0fe9%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-10%2F133632-896729.jpg&h=ac374887&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e4a28bba7ec6167d8963e25a5df500b0678cc85","tid":